high_descs: Go straight towards the TV, then left into the kitchen area, approaching the fridge straight ahead and to the left.
Remove the bar of soap from the fridge.
Turn left and follow the wall on the right, turning right to get into the bathroom.
Wash the bar of soap in the sink with water.
Look to the toilet next to the sink.
Place the soap bar on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Wash a bar of soap with water and place it on a toilet.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the fridge.
Pick the soap bar from the fridge.
Turn right and turn left to the sink.
Put the soap bar inside the sink and rinse it off.
Pick it back and turn left to the toilet.
Place the soap bar on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: To place the soap bar on the toilet.
